Aqua and Gold Watercolor Beach Thank You Card

Review Aqua and Gold Watercolor Beach Thank You Card – greeting cards Popular Aqua and Gold Watercolor Beach Thank You Card if you are looking for it, we recommend it Aqua and Gold Watercolor Beach Thank You Card There are many featuresThis aqua and gold watercolor beach thank you card is perfect for a tropical destination wedding. The simple and modern design features stunning turquoise, teal and light blue watercolor with a soft gold sparkle reminiscent of the sand and sea. It’s paired with gorgeous elegant calligraphy. The back of the card is blank, so you will have plenty of space to write a thoughtful personalized note. Customize the front of the card with your names. This card can be used for a wedding, bridal shower, or any special event.

Please Note: This design does not feature real gold glitter. It is a high quality graphic made to look like a shimmery gold sparkle. Price:$1.80
